# AI configuration for git-tools
# Shared across commit-ai-coauthor and other tools.
#
# To customize: copy this file to ~/.config/git-tools/ai-config
#
# Format: Name|email|default_model|model1,model2,model3,...
# - Name: display name for the AI
# - email: co-author email
# - default_model: default when selecting this AI
# - models: comma-separated list of popular models (for fzf selection)
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Add your own entries to extend the list.

